    "Moreover, Figs.",
    "Table 9 shows that ViT transformer outperforms the other networks, specifically the CNN-based ones.",
    "It can be noticed that model achieved competitive accuracy scores on the testing set with 95.65% in INbreast, 97.61% in CESM, and 80% in DM.",
    "Also, it provides the highest AUC score among the other experimented networks, it achieved 88%, 90%, and 70% in INbreast CESM and DM, respectively.",
